668
00:46:03,720 --> 00:46:04,200
Hanya...

669
00:46:05,480 --> 00:46:06,520
Yang asli.

670
00:46:08,480 --> 00:46:09,200
Cantik sekali.

671
00:46:14,600 --> 00:46:15,440
Terima kasih, North.

672
00:46:17,840 --> 00:46:18,720
Terima kasih.

673
00:46:20,480 --> 00:46:21,240
Sama-sama.

674
00:46:21,480 --> 00:46:22,120
Bukan apa-apa.

675
