693
00:48:43,440 --> 00:48:43,880
Hormat sedikit.

694
00:48:45,080 --> 00:48:46,240
Aku lebih tua darimu.

695
00:48:46,840 --> 00:48:47,880
Bisa dibilang orang yang lebih tua.

696
00:48:49,360 --> 00:48:49,840
Baik.

697
00:48:50,800 --> 00:48:51,400
Hormat.

698
00:48:53,600 --> 00:48:57,480
Begini saja.

699
00:48:59,840 --> 00:49:01,120
